Unless some asshole at Hillcrest decides
to sucker punch me in the hallway,

41:46.420 --> 41:47.922
but that's the...

41:48.631 --> 41:50.549
entirety of my human contact

41:51.050 --> 41:52.050
nowadays.

41:53.052 --> 41:57.014
Except for Melody, who provides a service
that you and I need.

42:02.019 --> 42:03.019
Alex.

42:11.820 --> 42:12.821
Go get 'em!

42:20.663 --> 42:23.499
Sweetie, slow down. You're not in a movie.

42:25.501 --> 42:26.502
Can we kiss?

42:26.961 --> 42:27.961
Okay.

42:39.098 --> 42:40.099
Shit. Sorry.

42:40.182 --> 42:41.725
No, you're good. You're good.

42:47.022 --> 42:48.399
- Sorry.
- All good.

42:49.191 --> 42:51.360
Talk to me. Talk dirty.

42:51.443 --> 42:52.278
No.

42:52.361 --> 42:53.445
Come on, stud.

42:54.446 --> 42:56.282
Talk to me. Tell me what's up.

42:56.365 --> 42:58.867
- I think I'm gonna come.
- That's it.

42:59.451 --> 43:00.536
Show me you're a man.

43:00.619 --> 43:02.746
Bitch! Fucking bitch!

43:25.561 --> 43:26.761
So, wait. Where are we?

43:27.730 --> 43:28.856
Finish your story.

43:28.939 --> 43:30.691
No, I just, I mean literally,

43:30.774 --> 43:33.861
the next night after we went
to fucking what's-her-name...

43:33.944 --> 43:35.613
The next night, I met her.

43:35.696 --> 43:39.033
She goes to East County, and we've been,
like, doing it every night this week.

43:39.116 --> 43:42.911
Dude, hell yeah! I'm honored you fit me
in to your busy schedule.

43:45.873 --> 43:47.958
She has to spend some time
with her boyfriend.

43:49.168 --> 43:51.253
Dude, what are we even doing here?

43:54.840 --> 43:56.300
It's my father's new place.

43:57.259 --> 44:00.763
He's in Telluride with his lady.
We're gonna go in and fuck the place up.

44:01.430 --> 44:04.099
- Dude, that's breaking and entering.
- No, he's my dad.

44:04.892 --> 44:07.144
Technically,
I'm just messing up my own place.

44:20.074 --> 44:21.074
Fuck.

44:28.248 --> 44:29.375
Oh, fuck, yes.

44:31.543 --> 44:32.544
That'll do it.

44:39.635 --> 44:40.719
Oh, hell yeah!

44:45.057 --> 44:46.308
Good call!

44:49.978 --> 44:51.438
